{"type":"article","id":13346,"title":"为防传染，安徽当涂县禁止打麻将","uid":25698,"topics":[3580,163,1,161,5262],"contents":"1月28日晚，新冠肺炎疫情当前，安徽马鞍山当涂县湖阳派出所进入村庄进行排查。当晚，民警共查获群众聚集打麻将行为十多起，当场砸毁麻将机16台，并立即将现场聚集人员驱散 ，并依法传唤训诫麻将机所有人。<br>\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Xhnsoc__Redflag/status/1222773894530174976\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Xhnsoc__Redflag/status/1222773894530174976<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Xhnsoc__Redflag/status/1222773894530174976/photo/1\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://twitter.com/Xhnsoc__Redflag/status/1222773894530174976/photo/1\" alt=\"https://twitter.com/Xhnsoc__Redflag/status/1222773894530174976/photo/1\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a></a>","date":"2020-01-30","agreeCount":2,"discussionCount":0}